item.title: US-20 West - Nebraska Medal of Honor Highway
item.description: Nebraska Medal of Honor Highway on US-20 west. US-20 is designated as a Medal of Honor highway. Each state along US-20 has designated its stretch of US-20 as a Medal of Honor highway. The signs across each state look similar.
